title: LibGuides: Traditional Sources: Naturopathy Collection
author: Gwyneth Bell
description: Access traditional sources direct from the library.
cleaned_text: The Naturopathy collection is a representation of seminal and origin texts with importance to contemporary Naturopathic practice. The Naturopathic Medicine Historical Collection includes digitized 19th-20th century publications on naturopathy, homeopathy, nutrition, and hygiene.
